caption.p: ( a) Top view, ( b) bottom view, and ( c,d) cross-section SEM images of an LTO self-standing film made of VGCF–COOH carbon obtained at magnifications of ( a,b) ×1000, ( c) ×3000, and ( d) ×4000. The inset in ( b) is a zoom-in image showing the intertwined carbon fibers. The red dots in ( c) identify the carbon current collector.
